        <h1 class="proj-title">How I Build<br>with AI</h1>
        <p class="proj-sub">"I use AI" is the most useless line in a 2026 portfolio — everyone says it. The interesting question is where you let it touch the work, and where you deliberately don't. Here's my actual line, and why I keep the LLM out of the product.</p>
